verbose_text: MCU-i4 and MCU-i11 decrease agonist induced InsP3 dependent mitochondrial Ca 2+ uptake in a MICU1 dependent manner, but they do not alter resting mitochondrial [Ca 2+], indicating that the gatekeeping role of MICU1 - MICU2 complex is maintained.
